  "raw_response": "{\n  \"title\": \"Bullish Change of Character after Breaking Major High and Mitigating All Supply Zones\",\n  \"school\": \"Smart Money Concepts (SMC)\",\n  \"asset\": null,\n  \"timeframe\": null,\n  \"market_context\": \"Price had formed a series of higher highs and higher lows, then broke below a swing low (CHOCH), swept liquidity, and subsequently reversed sharply upward—breaking above the most recent major high and all prior supply zones with no unmitigated supply remaining.\",\n  \"key_observation\": \"After breaking and closing above the major high, price eliminated all prior supply zones, automatically forming a new unmitigated demand zone at the breakout extreme, signaling a bullish trend shift.\",\n  \"analysis_steps\": [\n    \"Step 1: The analyst identified a prior bearish CHoCH (Change of Character) marked by a break below a swing low (HL) followed by a liquidity sweep.\",\n    \"Step 2: Price then broke and closed above the most recent major high, confirming a structural reversal.\",\n    \"Step 3: The analyst observed that all prior supply zones were mitigated (filled or invalidated) before the breakout, leaving no unmitigated supply behind.\",\n    \"Step 4: Based on the rule that a broken zone creates an opposite-side zone, the analyst concluded a new unmitigated demand zone formed at the breakout extreme.\",\n    \"Step 5: The analyst proposed entering a long trade via a buy limit order in the newly formed demand zone, expecting price to retrace, react, and resume upward.\"\n  ],\n  \"outcome\": null,\n  \"",
